    # rb "Oh naw, that's alright. I liked working on it and hanging out with y'all."
    rb "Oh nein, schon gut. Es hat mir Spaß gemacht, daran zu arbeiten und mit euch abzuhängen."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:645
translate german mari13nothreesome_8cca2575:

    # rb "And the food was great too."
    rb "Und das Essen war auch super."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:646
translate german mari13nothreesome_8efa9ce0:

    # fr "Alright. Well, you have my number if you ever want to talk or hang out or something."
    fr "Okay. Na ja, du hast meine Nummer, falls du mal reden oder etwas unternehmen willst oder so."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:647
translate german mari13nothreesome_0e8fd69e:

    # fr "I could always use a new girl friend."
    fr "Ich kann immer eine neue Freundin gebrauchen."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:648
translate german mari13nothreesome_8e3a433a:

    # rb "Oh yeah, we should do something sometime. That'd be fun."
    rb "Oh ja, wir sollten mal was zusammen machen. Das wäre lustig."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:650
translate german mari13nothreesome_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_surething2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_surething2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:651
translate german mari13nothreesome_9af4e82f:

    # fr "Sure thing!"
    fr "Klar doch!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:652
translate german mari13nothreesome_97bf71f7:

    # rb "Alright, I'll see y'all later. Have a good night!"
    rb "Okay, wir sehen uns später. Habt einen schönen Abend!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:653
translate german mari13nothreesome_e7b02c91:

    # pc "You too, Reba. Thanks again!"
    pc "Du auch, Reba. Nochmals vielen Dank!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:657
translate german mari13nothreesome_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_comeinside1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_comeinside1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:658
translate german mari13nothreesome_3d089295:

    # fr "So... do you want to come inside and spend some time with me?"
    fr "Also... willst du reinkommen und ein bisschen Zeit mit mir verbringen?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:663
translate german mari13nothreesome_9bd5a025:

    # "I go inside with her and help her clean up the kitchen, then things quickly lead to her bedroom."
    "Ich gehe mit ihr rein und helfe ihr, die Küche aufzuräumen, dann führt das Ganze schnell in ihr Schlafzimmer."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:672
translate german mari13nothreesome_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mari_aww2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_aww2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:673
translate german mari13nothreesome_e10a3ba0:

    # fr "Aw alright. I'll see you later then, [pcname]."
    fr "Ach okay. Dann bis später, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:676
translate german mari13nothreesome_cb6284dc:

    # "We say our goodbyes and I get in my car and drive away."
    "Wir verabschieden uns, ich steige in mein Auto und fahre los."

translate german strings:

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:3
    old "The weekend after you go with Mari to the cemetery to visit her parents, she will call you asking for your help."
    new "Am Wochenende, nachdem du mit Mari zum Friedhof gegangen bist, um ihre Eltern zu besuchen, wird sie dich anrufen und um deine Hilfe bitten."

    # game/Scenes/Mari/mari13.rpy:4
    old "You can only help her with her problem after you have learned about Reba's job. At that point, you can call Mari on the weekend and tell her that you have a friend who could help. Both Reba and Mari's hearts need to be turned on."
    new "Du kannst ihr erst helfen, wenn du von Rebas Job erfahren hast. Dann kannst du Mari am Wochenende anrufen und ihr sagen, dass du eine Freundin hast, die helfen könnte. Sowohl Rebas als auch Maris Herz müssen dafür offen sein."

